quiz.question:
What is the time complexity of the following code snippet?

X = 1;
Y = 2;
Z = X + Y;
Print Z;

Identify the time complexity for the following code snippet:

X = 20;
If (X <= 10) {
    print X;
}

What is the time complexity of the following code snippet?

Int i;
i = 0;
For (i=0; i<n; i++) {
    Print i;
}

Consider the following code:

Int i;
i=0;
For (i=0; i<n; i++) { // Loop 1
    Print i;
}
For (int j=0; j<n; j++) { // Loop 2
    For (int k=0; k<n; k++) { // Loop 3
        Print j+k;
    }
}

What is the dominant time complexity of this entire code block?

What is the time complexity of the following code snippet?

Int i;
i=1;
For (i=1; i<n; i*=2) {
    Print i;
}

What is the time complexity of the following code snippet?

Int i, j;
i=j=0;
For (i=0; i<n; i++) {
    For (j=1; j<n; j=j*3) {
        Print i + j;
    }
}

What is the overall time complexity of the following code?

Int i;
i=0;
For (i=0; i<n; i++) { // Loop A
    Print i;
}
For (int j=1; j<n; j=j*3) { // Loop B
    Print j;
}

What is the time complexity of the following pseudo-code?

result = 0;
for (i = 0; i < n / 2; i++) {
    result += i;
}
